				<title>Awwww...</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12267666/scp-4468#post-4850487</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 22 Dec 2020 00:09:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ISNorden</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6966599</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I've always dreamed of having a teddy bear that can send/receive long-distance hugs; it's a shame that something so lovable has a tragic twist! Well-written documentation though; here's a non-anomalous hug to go with my upvote. 🫂</p> 
				 	]]>
