					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12267666#post-4489882</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12267666/scp-4468#post-4489882</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2020 05:44:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>CeilYurei</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6021092</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>No, what is implied is his soul was linked to the bear, so the parents could remotely hug their child&#8230;but it drastically reduces their lifespan, hence why the current Dr WOndertainment discontinued the line. Even if the children are terminally ill, a guaranteed death sentence in 3 weeks removes any hope, which is drastically against the Wondertainment brand of trying to spread whimsy.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
